Third-party components
----------------------

This repository keeps selected third-party data-source libraries and binary
runtime files under lib/ to reduce version drift and make the project easier
to run in controlled environments. Those components remain governed by their
own licenses and upstream terms. The StockDataMaster license does not change
the license, ownership, or usage restrictions of third-party components.

Before redistributing a derived package or using this repository in a
commercial environment, review the licensing and service terms for every data
source and client library you enable, including but not limited to Tushare,
Baostock, Mootdx, and xtquant/QMT.

Demo credentials
----------------

The Tushare value shipped in config.json is an invalidated demo key retained
for documentation and configuration-shape compatibility. Users should provide
their own token through the repository-local .env file or a private runtime
environment variable.
